import React from 'react'
import Video from '../../videos/hd0090.mov'
import {
    HeroContainer,
    HeroBg,
    VideoBg,
    HeroContent,
    HeroH1,
    HeroP,
    HeroBtnWrapper,
    ArrowForward,
    ArrowRight
} from './HeroSectionElement';

const HeroSection = () => {
    return (
        <HeroContainer>
            <HeroBg>
                <VideoBg autoPlay loop muted src={Video} type='video/mp4' />
            </HeroBg>
            <HeroContent>
                <HeroH1>A Time Machine for Personal Knowledge</HeroH1>
                <HeroP>Sign up now to become one of our first 500 free BETA users</HeroP>
            </HeroContent>
        </HeroContainer>
    )
}

export default HeroSection
